cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.IT

This paper deals with the complexity measure of deep neural networks and its application in neural architecture search. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also focuses on vision models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper uses quantum statistical mechanics, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper involves computation, which could place it in cs.IT (Information Theory).
